WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.233 --> 00:00:01.266
It is like that.

2
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.933
Don’t be so selfish, okay?

3
00:00:03.266 --> 00:00:04.466
Our child is still young.

4
00:00:04.466 --> 00:00:06.100
Is resigning such a small thing

5
00:00:06.166 --> 00:00:07.366
something you can’t do?

6
00:00:08.266 --> 00:00:08.833
No.

7
00:00:09.833 --> 00:00:10.300
I can’t.

8
00:00:11.466 --> 00:00:12.633
Let me go.

9
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:13.600
Jian Dao,

10
00:00:13.966 --> 00:00:15.366
come back to me, okay?

11
00:00:15.433 --> 00:00:16.666
You give me the company,

12
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:17.900
and I’ll return the child to you.

13
00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.533
Can’t we live happily

14
00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:20.666
together again?

15
00:00:22.533 --> 00:00:23.200
Zhang Wen Xu,

16
00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.433
stop dreaming.

17
00:00:24.933 --> 00:00:27.033
Don’t take my kindness for granted, Jian Dao.

18
00:00:27.633 --> 00:00:28.500
What are you planning to do?

19
00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:34.333
Get out!

20
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:36.800
Li Bei Qīng,

21
00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:37.266
It’s okay,

22
00:00:37.266 --> 00:00:37.766
I’m here.

23
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:41.400
Li Bei Qīng,

24
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:43.433
Who let you in?

25
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:44.933
Zhang Wen Xu,

26
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:46.266
you have no shame.

27
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:48.566
Using a child to threaten a mother,

28
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.000
doesn’t Jian Dao

29
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:52.200
deserve to have her own life?

30
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:54.866
Even if you’re the president of Li Shi Group,

31
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:55.933
this is still my family matter.

32
00:00:55.933 --> 00:00:57.400
It’s not your place to interfere.

33
00:00:58.166 --> 00:00:59.566
I’ll handle this.
